# Futuristic Shop Management System

A desktop-based shop management application developed using Python, CustomTkinter, and SQLite.

## Features
- Admin and Cashier Login
- Product Management
- Customer Management
- Employee Management
- Billing System
- Sales Tracking
- Invoice Generation

## Technologies Used
- Python
- CustomTkinter
- SQLite
- Tabulate

## Installation
pip install -r requirements.txt

python BILLER.py

